            "value": "该网站要求使用通行密钥 (Passkey) 验证，但应用内浏览器暂不支持。请使用密码或短信等其他方式登录。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This will package and send the current session state to the requester. Please confirm you have completed login or the required actions.": {
